The paper deals with image processing using a neural network architecture, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of neural networks for learning and prediction also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves graphics and visualization techniques, which are covered under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
